Adobe Systems Inc. said Monday that it will not release new versions of its Creative Suite software package. Instead, the maker of Photoshop, Illustrator and Acrobat, is shifting focus to Creative Cloud, which makes its software available through a monthly subscription that starts at $50 for an individual. (AP Photo/Paul Sakuma, File)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Adobe Creative Could]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Hackers claim it only took a 10-minute phone call to shut down MGM Resorts]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>根据<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/vxunderground/status/1701758864390050145?s=46&amp;t=mOWjpAvBR_EgMxB3MbSPxw">恶意软件存档 vx-underground</a>发布的帖子，ALPHV/BlackCat 勒索软件组织声称对周二<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/mgm-resorts-hit-by-cybersecurity-issue-leading-to-massive-outage-215205561.html">米高梅度假村的网络中断</a>负责。该组织声称使用了常见的社会工程策略，或获得员工的信任来获取内部信息，试图从米高梅度假村获取赎金，但据报道该公司拒绝支付。据该组织称，授予初始访问权限的对话只花了 10 分钟。</p><p>该组织在 X 上的一篇帖子中写道：“ALPHV 勒索软件组织为危害米高梅度假村所做的一切都是在 LinkedIn 上查找员工，然后致电服务台。”这些详细信息来自 ALPHV，但尚未得到安全研究人员的独立证实。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这家国际连锁度假村本周早些时候开始出现停电，因为顾客注意到<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://finance.yahoo.com/news/mgm-resorts-hack-fallout-includes-001920146.html">拉斯维加斯大道上米高梅度假村旗下赌场的老虎机被关闭</a>。截至周三上午，米高梅度假村仍显示出正在经历停机的迹象，例如网站持续中断。米高梅度假村尚未回应置评请求，但<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/MGMResortsIntl/status/1701443388086825231">在周二的一份声明中</a>表示，“我们的度假村，包括餐饮、娱乐和博彩目前正在运营。” </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/2cc56cd0-523e-11ee-8f26-e78083aa9f95" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/2cc56cd0-523e-11ee-8f26-e78083aa9f95" style="height:720px;width:1774px;" alt="周三早上，米高梅度假村的主页仍然显示该网站无法访问。" data-uuid="61418337-b1d8-3fa3-840a-84a2baddf9d3"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">凯蒂·马龙为 Engadget 拍摄</div></figure><p>据 vx-underground 称，ALPHV 在网络安全界享有盛誉，因为“在初始访问的社会工程方面具有非凡的天赋”。从那里开始，它通常使用 <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.mandiant.com/resources/blog/alphv-ransomware-backup">勒索软件策略</a>来勒索目标支付费用，并且它一直在追捕大型企业目标。 7 月，ALPHV 和另一位威胁参与者 Clop <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/est-e-lauder-beauty-giant-breached-by-two-ransomware-gangs/">在其数据泄露网站上列出了美容巨头雅诗兰黛 (Estée Lauder)</a> 。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/hackers-claim-it-only-took-a-10-minute-phone-call-to-shutdown-mgm-resorts-143147493.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/hackers-claim-it-only-took-a-10-minute-phone-call-to-shutdown-mgm-resorts-143147493.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 810b72d0-2cad-41cf-a6e2-f220981a28b5</guid><dc:creator>凯蒂·马龙</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 13 Sep 2023 14:31:47 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694615556</ingested><modified> 2023-09-13T14:32:42+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Professional Services]]></category><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Katie Malone]]></category><media:content height="900" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/457014c0-523d-11ee-8f6b-71de2d5f7e12" width="1200"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="900" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/457014c0-523d-11ee-8f6b-71de2d5f7e12" width="1200">